          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。孟良上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伽山太保显英豪，昼夜巡边不惮劳。饶尔番兵千百万，撞着咱，胆战魂魄消。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺孟良，奉着哥哥将令，巡察界河，一路平安无事，不免回复哥哥将令，须索\n走遭也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（粉蝶儿） 这些时无处征伐，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺在那界河边，恰才巡罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "涌彪躯舒猿臂，肝横胆乍。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回头儿只看咱全身披挂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是辕门，为何这等静悄悄地？\n呔！里面哪个小校在？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孟将军回来了，巡查界河多有辛苦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小校，禀知元帅，说俺孟良巡查界河一路平安无事，俺今特来交令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅与岳将军在后帐议论紧急军情，用你不着，叫你回避。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用哪个不着？"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用你不着。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫哪个回避？"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫你回避。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！小校吃我一斧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请元帅，啊呀杀人！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨延昭、岳胜同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪个在此杀人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哇呀……"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳胜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢无礼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哇呀……\n恁兄弟奉着哥哥将令，巡查界河，一路平安无事，俺今特来交令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟多有辛苦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好说。方才那一小校说，元帅与岳将军在后帐议论紧急军情，用俺不着，叫俺\n回避，俺故此吓他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此话是我对他说的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳胜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果有此话。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀，果有此话？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟，我这里用你不着，你自回避。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用哪个不着？"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳胜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用你不着。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫哪个回避？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫你回避。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀，哥呀！你今番就是杀了俺，也是偏不回避的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岳贤弟，你看孟良哪知我的心事来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳胜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红绣鞋） 往常时，无我来不喜欢说话，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日个，见俺来便低着头无语使这嗟呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红绣鞋） 有甚么机密事，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对孟良也合知么。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（岳胜与杨延昭耳语。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红绣鞋） 一个儿眼角觑，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他哪里知道？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孟良 （红绣鞋） 一个儿脚尖踏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "噫！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红绣鞋） 好教俺半合儿傒幸杀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳胜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孟贤弟，元帅有件心事命你猜来，猜着用你，猜不着你自回避。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅有心事，命俺猜来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳胜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗨！待俺猜来，待俺猜来，待俺猜来，俺今番猜着了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳胜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猜着何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吖呵喏！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（石榴花） 莫不是大辽兵马前来蹅踏，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺与你火速地便去争杀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳胜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孟良 （石榴花） 莫不是王枢密搬弄着、搬弄着宋官家，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺与你急忙备马便去京华。"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳胜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（石榴花） 莫不是佘太君定有人便相欺压，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孟贤弟，我的老母谁敢欺压！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吖咳，着啊！量他们确也不敢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（石榴花） 则除非赵玄坛威力无加，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "才敢把虎头儿须来抓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺与你亲自把贼拿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孟贤弟，我要取一物，他那里兵多将广，只怕你一人取他不来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那厮他！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（斗鹌鹑） 又不是布雾的蚩尤，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又不是飞天、飞天的夜叉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "藏在了藏在了地下。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若见他，说那厮能变化。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吼一吼！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（斗鹌鹑） 骨碌碌海沸山崩，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "觑一觑，觑一觑天摧地塌。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孟贤弟，量你也猜不着。待愚兄对你说了吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的哥，请讲，请讲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昨夜偶得一梦，梦得我父老元戎托梦于我，说被番兵困在虎口交牙峪，只困得\n内无粮草，外无救兵，我父差七郎兄弟前到雄关搬兵求救，不想被潘仁美乱箭\n射死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哇呀……我的哥，请讲，请讲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那时我父盼兵不到，盼子不归，无奈碰死在李陵碑下。尸骨被番兵盗去，吊在\n幽州昊天塔上，每日用一百个小番，各射一箭，名曰百箭会。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哇呀……请讲，请讲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那时我父幽魂疼痛难忍，来在三关渡口，托我一梦，叫我盗取爹爹骨殖而归。\n是我无计可施，故此伤感吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的哥，我想这件事，别人去不得，恁兄弟我倒也去得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你去不得。你……"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊……"
        },
        {
          "character": "岳胜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不能！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（上小楼） 凭着俺烧天火把，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说什么经忏佛法。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿住和尚，揝定袈裟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "滴溜溜噗！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（上小楼） 脑袋儿殿前阶下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孟贤弟，你若拿住那厮便怎样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我若拿住他！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（上小楼） 胸脯上脚去蹬，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "面门上把来抓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乞抽扢叉、斫他鼻凹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我直着释迦佛也整理不下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟执意要去，可带多少人马？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟良",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
